OL,3,CMum left 'traumatised' after gang in
OL,4,Cbalaclavas break into home
OL,6,FA mother has said she's been left
OL,7,F"traumatised" after a gang in
OL,8,Fbalaclavas broke into her home while
OL,9,Fher young son was in bed asleep.
OL,11,FThe group of men smashed into the
OL,12,Fhouse on Celandine Rise in Swinton, ,
OL,13,Fat around 10.30pm on Wednesday, 31
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FStacey Wood said she had been in bed
OL,17,Fwith her young son at the time when
OL,18,Fshe heard the group smash through the
OL,19,Fside door of her house with a brick.
