OL,3,CMum left 'traumatised' after gang in
OL,4,Cbalaclavas break into home
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "I kept saying my
OL,7,Fbaby is in the bedroom and they're
OL,8,Fscaring him, so for them to carry on
OL,9,Fis just brutal.
OL,11,F"It's brutal what they've done."
OL,13,FThe group of men stole Stacey's car
OL,14,Fand demanded her to give the keys to
OL,15,Fher partner's car, but she refused.
OL,17,F"They did not care that I was a woman
OL,18,Fon my own, that I had my son. They
OL,19,Fjust did not care. It was just
OL,20,Fruthless.
