OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "It is understood
OL,7,Fthat one of the men then drove away in
OL,8,Fthe Citroen C3, while a further man
OL,9,Fapproached the front door of the
OL,10,Fproperty and demanded the keys for a
OL,11,Fsecond vehicle on the drive.
OL,13,F"The man was unsuccessful in his
OL,14,Fattempts to steal the keys and then
OL,15,Ffled the scene on foot.
OL,17,F"No arrests have been made at this
OL,18,Ftime but enquiries into the incident
OL,19,Fare ongoing."
